[{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"CurrentModule = Parameters2JSON","category":"page"},{"location":"#Parameters2JSON","page":"Home","title":"Parameters2JSON","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Documentation for Parameters2JSON.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Modules = [Parameters2JSON]","category":"page"},{"location":"#Parameters2JSON.export_json-Tuple{Any, Any}","page":"Home","title":"Parameters2JSON.export_json","text":"export_json(mystruct, fl; openmode=\"w\")\n\nWrites the @jsonable struct mystruct to a file fl.\n\nAdditional Information\n\nWrapper around JSON3.pretty(::IO, mystruct).\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#Parameters2JSON.import_json-Union{Tuple{T}, Tuple{Any, Type{T}}} where T","page":"Home","title":"Parameters2JSON.import_json","text":"import_json(fl, ::Type{T})\n\nReads from a file fl into a @jsonable struct of type T.\n\nAdditional Information\n\nWrapper around JSON3.read(::String, T ).\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#Parameters2JSON.import_json_and_display-Union{Tuple{T}, Tuple{Any, Type{T}}, Tuple{Any, Type{T}, IO}} where T","page":"Home","title":"Parameters2JSON.import_json_and_display","text":"import_json_and_display(fl, ::Type{T}, io::IO = stdout)\n\nReads from a file fl into a @jsonable struct of type T and calls pretty_display on the result.\n\nAdditional Information\n\nI think I'll destroy this function and merge it into import_json as a different method.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#Parameters2JSON.pretty_display-Tuple{Any}","page":"Home","title":"Parameters2JSON.pretty_display","text":"pretty_display(params)\n\nWrites the @jsonable struct params to an stdout.\n\nAdditional Information\n\nFurther prettifies a call to JSON3.pretty(stdout, params).\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#Parameters2JSON.pretty_display-Tuple{IO, Any}","page":"Home","title":"Parameters2JSON.pretty_display","text":"pretty_display(io::IO, params)\n\nWrites the @jsonable struct params to an IO stream.\n\nAdditional Information\n\nFurther prettifies a call to JSON3.pretty(::IO, params).\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#Parameters2JSON.pretty_display-Tuple{String, Any}","page":"Home","title":"Parameters2JSON.pretty_display","text":"pretty_display(str::String, params)\n\nWrites the @jsonable struct params to a string str and returns it.\n\nAdditional Information\n\nFurther prettifies a call to JSON3.pretty(::IO, params).\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#Parameters2JSON.pretty_display-Tuple{Type{String}, Any}","page":"Home","title":"Parameters2JSON.pretty_display","text":"pretty_display(::Type{String}, params)\n\nWrites the @jsonable struct params to a string and returns it.\n\nAdditional Information\n\nFurther prettifies a call to JSON3.pretty(::IO, params).\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#Parameters2JSON.@jsonable-Tuple{Any}","page":"Home","title":"Parameters2JSON.@jsonable","text":"@jsonable [mutable] struct Foo ... end\n\nConvenience macro allowing JSON import, exports, and displays for structs.\n\nAdditional Information\n\nOne must have the StructTypes package Pkg.added in order to use any JSON functionality.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"macro"}]
